title: Santa Griz'n Episode 1
description: The Santa Cruz team visits Emmanuel Guzman in his stomping grounds, beautiful Santa Cruz California. Day 1: Santa Cruz Skatepark and the legendary Buena Vista pool. Featuring Shuriken Shannon, Justin Strubing, Josh Borden, Salba, Cody Chapman, and Sid Melvin.
